        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-01-02 10:15:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAs [~mrichomme] wants to use pnf_registration tag for smoke tests (no real/available Open Stack connected to ONAP) using xtesting tool there is need to correct following items in pnf_registration test:\n- create region, cloud owner, tenant based on variables from robot_properties.py file\n- create own:   lineOfBusiness, platform, project, owningEntity \n- create separate keyword for PNF customer creation, independent from availability of connectivity to  real/available Open Stack. Keyword should use variables from robot_properties.py\n\nPlease look at my changes I hope that are acceptable.\nWhen PNF will be switched to building blocks and new VID GUI then I hope pnf_registration tests will be simplified.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
