        "timestamp": "2020-01-03 00:15:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(4 comments)\n\nI've added my comments and made changes in code.\nAdditionally I decided to create dummy tenant for PNF Orchestartion in AAI with name different (unique) then defined in robot_properties.py.\nI did that because I don't want to have conflict between \"pnf_registartion\" and \"init\" tags.\n\"pnf_registartion\" adds entry to AAI without checking of tenant id at real Open Stack however \"init\" does that.\nWhen \"pnf_registartion\" would add this entry and \"init\" would be executed after \"pnf_registarion\" then \"init\" will not correct tenant id in AAI and any VNF Orchestartion will fail.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
